                                        "Item": "Num 9.3.ii",
                                        "Section": "2.6",
                                        "Cited_Guidance": "Supplemental Qualifier datasets for split domains would also be split. The nomenclature will include the additional one to two characters used to identify the split dataset (e.g., SUPPLBHM, SUPPFACM)."
                                    }
                                ],
                                "Origin": "TIG Conformance Rules",
